lender.occupational_info:
With a professional, friendly approach and confidential treatment, Laser Spa Group combines the art of healing with a sophisticated appreciation of aesthetics. We understand the subtle relationship between looking one's best and feeling one's best and we are acutely aware of the power of perception and it's significant contribution to the client's overall feeling of wellness.
Laser Spa Group Mission Statement:
* Provide thorough and comprehensive consultations including detailed explanations on why we recommend specific services and give realistic expectations of the result of these treatments. This will include a complete skin care program as well as a program for caring for your skin at home.
* We will treat each of our clients in a pleasant and professional manner. We will strive to make our place of business one which is enjoyable to visit and one in which you will feel comfortable referring friends and family.
* We will earn your business! We are aware that you have many choices for aesthetic services. Through our experienced staff, state-of-the-art lasers and equipment, advanced services and our integrity, we will provide you with a level of service superior to not only our competition here in Hamilton, but anywhere in the country.
Our area of expertise is Laser Hair Removal and have been open since 2003. We provide a Laser Rental Program for Physicians, Clinics, Salons and Spas, and a research-friendly website detailing information in all aspects of laser hair removal, brazilian waxing, hair growth cycles, hair growth disorders, and frequently asked questions. Bozana has recently developed a 40 hour Laser & IPL Training course. Laser Spa Group training courses are being designed to prepare the graduating student for the medical based aesthetic market. Courses are designed for those students with appropriate prerequisites, including aestheticians, nurses, cosmetologists, and physicians. Laser Home Parties are also available.
Laser Spa Group has also been nominated for the Reader's Choice Awards for favourite Laser Hair Removal Business three years in a row. Laser Spa Group won the Platinum award in 2008 (first place), and Diamind in 2009 (second), and Platinum again in 2010. Bozana has recently been Nominated Favourite Aesthetician and Favourite Medical Aesthetican 2010, Favourite Spa & Aesthetics as well as Favourite Laser Hair Removal 2010. Bozana is an active member of the ASLMS (the American Sociey for Laser Medicine and Surgery) and the SCMHR (The Society for Clinical and Medical Hair Removal). Bozana's Biography has also been published and featured in the ABI - The American Biographical Institute's - Great Women of the 21st Century 2006 Edition.
